OL,3,CPat Finucane public inquiry 'a
OL,4,Cwatershed moment,' says widow
OL,6,FGeraldine Finucane said she believed
OL,7,Fthe public inquiry into her husband's
OL,8,Fmurder could be a "watershed moment"
OL,9,Fin dealing with legacy cases.
OL,11,FThe UK Government has ordered a public
OL,12,Finquiry into the collusion-linked
OL,13,Floyalist paramilitary murder of
OL,14,FBelfast solicitor Pat Finucane in 1989.
OL,16,FMr Finucane, 39, was shot dead at his
OL,17,Ffamily home in north Belfast in
OL,18,FFebruary 1989 by the Ulster Defence
OL,19,FAssociation in an attack found by a
OL,20,Fseries of probes to have involved
OL,21,Fcollusion with the state.
