OL,3,CPat Finucane public inquiry 'a
OL,4,Cwatershed moment,' says widow
OL,6,FHis widow Geraldine and the couple's
OL,7,Fthree children have been campaigning
OL,8,Ffor decades for a public inquiry to
OL,9,Festablish the extent of security force
OL,10,Finvolvement.
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,13,Fmade the announcement to the House of
OL,14,FCommons.
OL,16,FThe minister said it is a "plain fact"
OL,17,Fthat a UK government commitment made
OL,18,Fmore than 20 years ago to hold an
OL,19,Finquiry into Mr Finucane's murder
OL,20,F"remains unfulfilled".
